Hi everyone!

I've been looking for quite some time for prints of Uesugi and Takeda.  
There are 2 in particular that I've been after but I can't seem to find any 
website or local store (Kansas City, MO) to purchase.  The Uesugi print 
shows him facing forward on a stool, he has a mostache in this print.  It 
looks rather basic, I'm sorry that I can't describe it any better but it's 
been a long time since I've seen a picture of it and don't remember the 
details.  The Takeda print shows him facing away on a deerskin stool looking 
at Mt. Fuji.  He's wearing a red cape.  If anyone knows where I could shop 
in this area, or point me to a webstore, I'd appreciate it!

Chuck
